title: New Creator: Tim and Barry
body:
[Bio]
For the past 20 years, Tim & Barry have redefined a multitude of creative disciplines, that range from shooting award-winning photography and video, to curating ground-breaking live music events. They are feted for their idiosyncratic, arguably eccentric, approach to creating and documenting contemporary cultural movements. Moving into crypto makes perfect sense as they are renown for innovating in the digital space, through projects such as their No Miming Freestyle series as well as Just Jam, their pioneering live stream.

[Use Cases]
Distribution
Soft Launch - We plan to announce the coin before the official launch via our socials to gain hype.
YouTube premieres - Using the launch of our new freestyle series we will give away $TAB at the end of the episode video premieres on YouTube.

Holding Mechanics
Exclusive content - We plan to give $TAB Coin holders exclusive previews of new content and allow them to nominate their favourite new musicians for the series.
Live event access - On the return of our live Just Jam events we plan to reward $TAB holders with exclusive access to events, as well as top holders being invited to intimate studio recordings.

Transactions
Remix competitions - With the release of freestyles we will also hold a remix competition, audio stems of the recording will be available to producers for purchase via $TAB. Best track wins - simple!
Merchandise & NFT sales - Paying in $TAB will allow for purchase of exclusive merchandise drops from our store as well as early access to NFT bidding/purchases.

[Grant Tier]
$1000

A 'yes' approves Tim & Barry, and a $1000 gift coin treasury grant
A 'no' denies this prop
